# House of Morvegil, Dukes of Harithilien after the Kinstrife
# House of Nepos, second Dukes of Harithilien, lords of boths sides of the Poros
# House of Tiridon, cadet of Telengaur, later lords of the Haithilien highlands.

# House of Anárionath

lineofanarion1 = {
	name = An_arion

	dynasty = dynasty_anarion
	religion = faith_edain
	culture = dunedain
	dna = anarion_dna			  

	father = lineofelendil
	mother = wifeofelendil	

	diplomacy = 4
	martial = 12
	stewardship = 10
	intrigue = 4
	learning = 8

	
	trait = education_stewardship_4
	trait = architect
	trait = unyielding_defender
	trait = calm
	trait = brave
	trait = temperate
	trait = born_on_numenor

	trait = blood_of_numenor_10
	3811.2.12 = {
		birth = yes
		effect = {
			learn_language = language_sindarin	
			learn_language = language_quenya
		}
	}
	3862.6.6 = {
		add_spouse = wifeofanarion
	}
	3912.1.1 = { #Gondor is established
		effect = {
			set_realm_capital = title:c_osgiliath
			#title:e_gondor = { #Juke note: do this in title history
			#	set_capital_county = title:c_osgiliath
			#}
		}
	}
	4032.4.17 = {
		death = { death_reason = death_battle }
	}
}

###################################
#### The Lords of Gardhon Fuir ####
###################################
# House of Rodirionath (Name TBD) 
# Rulers of Gardhon Fuir, originally descendend from a Prince of Anarion's line, who married a Northman woman and was disinherited by his father Prince Minastan. The line was istead given land in the North-March of Anorien, and was known for occasionally marrying across the border later. It went through the female line at least once. 
# A cadet formed when an Elder daughter of the family married the second son of the Duke of Eastfold. They ruled Halifirien for many years, eventaully taking the mantle of the Eastfold until the Rohirrim arived. Then, the line unlanded for a while, until one of it's sons married back into the main line around 2800, as it had died out. 

linebenrodir1 = { # Son of Minastir, married a Nothman woman and disinherited. 
    name = Benrodir
	dna = benrodir_i_dna

    dynasty = dynasty_anarion
    religion = faith_edain
    culture = gondorian

    sexuality = heterosexual

	father = lineofanarion36

    trait = humble
    trait = content
    trait = stubborn

	trait = intellect_good_2

    diplomacy = 18
    martial = 16
    stewardship = 15
    intrigue = 6
    learning = 12
    prowess = 14

    trait = education_stewardship_4


	trait = blood_of_numenor_7

    5618.10.11 = {
        birth = yes
    }

    5675.6.1 = {
        add_spouse = linebenrodir2
		set_relation_soulmate = character:linebenrodir2
		dynasty = dynasty_benrodir
		trait = disinherited
    }

    5836.9.15 = { #218
        death = { death_reason = death_natural_causes }
    }
}

# House of Palantirith

linepalantir1 = {
	name = Palantir # Stewards of edhellond
	dynasty = dynasty_serelond
	religion = faith_edain
	culture = gondorian

	
	trait = education_learning_4
	trait = intellect_good_3
	trait = diligent

#### House of Morvegil #### 
# Lords of Bar Morvegil, raised after the Kin-strife from a distant relative of Nepos who sided with Eldacar. (Nepos did not). Claimed Nepos's titles and ruled them as Duke of Harithilien until c. 2750, when they were stripped by Beregond for incompetence and disolyalty. Members survived until the War of the Ring. 

lineofmorvegilfinal = { 
	name = Malgalad # Last Duke of the line, lost his titles due to incompetence in the face of Haradric Invasion. 

	religion = faith_edain
	culture = gondorian
	dynasty = dynasty_morvegil

    father = lineofmorvegil136
    mother = lineofmorvegil137

	diplomacy = 2
	martial = 4
	stewardship = 8
	intrigue = 8
	learning = 5
	prowess = 5

	trait = education_stewardship_1
	trait = callous
	trait = craven
	trait = lazy

# House of Nendil the first lords of Neporos & the second Governors of Harondor

linenendilionath = {
	name = Nendil

	dynasty = dynasty_nendilionath
	religion = faith_edain
	culture = gondorian

	trait = brave

# Line of Borothor Local Danaine lord who assimilated to Gondorian more than others, Powerful count ruling over areas that in 2000 years becomes Edoras
lineofborothor1 = {
    name = Kolah

    dynasty = dynasty_borothorionath
    religion = faith_edain
    culture = danaine

    sexuality = heterosexual

    trait = physique_good_2
    trait = strong

    trait = brave
    trait = just
    trait = diligent

    trait = education_martial_4

    trait = cavalry_leader

    4001.5.10 = {
        birth = yes
        effect = {
			learn_language = language_sindarin
		}
    }

    4021.6.20 = {
        name = Borothor
        add_spouse = lineofborothor2
        set_relation_soulmate = character:lineofborothor2
    }

    4080.1.6 = {
        death = { death_reason = death_natural_causes }
    }
}

                        # He Writes Lairë Lírë or the summer song is an Ancient Book of westerness, intricately silver-bound, that tells many tales of the lost summer of humanity, and the simple beauty and good of life both grand and small.
